title: Ann Arbor’s Year in Crime, 2008
name: Ann Arbor’s Year in Crime, 2008
description:
Summary of crime in the city of Ann Arbor, Michigan - shared from the Ann Arbor Chronicle.

The first two weeks of January and the last two weeks of December are not included. So the data presented here should not be considered complete or official.
